{
  "doc_id": "22698",
  "text": "Generative Adversarial Networks (GANs) GANs are characterized by their powerful capability in data generation. Ian Goodfellow first introduced this adversarial framework [CITATION_1] , and within a few years following researchers have showed state-of-the-art performance among a wide range of applications [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] [CITATION_4] [CITATION_5] [CITATION_6] . We adopt GANs here to generate realistic adversarial examples that look alike real ones.",
